Arrow Transformation Test
-----------------------

This file tests the arrow transformation feature.

Arrow Notations:

→ Right arrow should transform to →
← Left arrow should transform to ←
↑ Up arrow should transform to ↑
↓ Down arrow should transform to ↓

Multiple arrows on one line: → and ← and ↑ and ↓

Arrows in code blocks (should not transform):

    → This is in a code block
    ← This is in a code block
    ↑ This is in a code block
    ↓ This is in a code block

End of test file.

